renewed-contributions.title: The Problems of Space Flying
renewed-contributions.note: There was no renewal filed for this story; however, it is a translation of 'Das Problem der Befahrung des Weltraums', originally published in German in 1928 and likely to have an active copyright due to GATT restoration.
